cs.SI, cs.SD, cs.SOC, cs.CYBER, cs.CR 

This paper deals with the analysis of social media networks and the spread of disinformation, which falls under the categories of social networks (cs.SI), social and information networks (cs.SD), and social computing (cs.SOC). Additionally, the paper discusses the use of bots and echo chambers in the spread of disinformation, which relates to cybersecurity (cs.CYBER) and cryptography and security (cs.CR).
